どんまいなんて言うの待っちゃうし　もーだめ
I'm waiting for you to say "never mind"... geez, no good

531
00:37:51,705 --> 00:37:56,105
エコするとかしないとか　片付け何とかしてほしいとか
Whether to be eco-friendly or not, or wanting the cleanup taken care of...

532
00:37:56,105 --> 00:38:00,305
幸せをどっちが描けるか賭ける毎日
A daily gamble on which of us can depict happiness

533
00:38:00,905 --> 00:38:05,105
卵焼きは控えるとか　明日からマジメにやるとか
Cutting back on tamagoyaki, or starting to take things seriously tomorrow...

