Thank you, Rushia-chan! I'm so happy, seriously. Thank you so much for coming today.

548
00:39:12,105 --> 00:39:14,305
祝えて良かったー！
I'm glad I could celebrate with you!

549
00:39:14,605 --> 00:39:17,605
お祝いできて嬉しい、ありがとうね、シオン先輩呼んでくれて。
I'm happy I could celebrate. Thank you for inviting me, Shion-senpai.

550
00:39:17,605 --> 00:39:22,605
マジでさっきまでさ、一人でさ、お誕生日パーティーしてたんだよね、実は。
Actually, until just now, I was having a birthday party by myself.

