572
00:40:21,117 --> 00:40:23,117
いや嬉しいマジで。 もっと増やしてこう。
I'm really happy. Let's do it more.

573
00:40:23,217 --> 00:40:26,117
増やしてこう。 増やしてこう、これからも。
Let's do it more. Let's do it more from now on too.

574
00:40:26,317 --> 00:40:29,117
ね、前回はさ、secret base だったよね。
Hey, last time was 'secret base', wasn't it?

575
00:40:29,217 --> 00:40:30,117
歌ったね！
We sang that!

